Fox ID: 10576084 Which Netflix Original stars Taylor Schilling, Laura Prepon, and Danielle Brooks? Guess I give up! Orange is the New Black OITNB Orange is the New Black ! What was the name of the movie that Emma Stone and Ryan Gosling first starred in together? Guess I give up! Crazy, Stupid, Love Crazy Stupid Love Crazy, Stupid, Love ! La La Land equalled All About Eve 's record for the most Oscar nominations, with 14. What’s the name of the only other movie to also receive 14 nominations? Guess I give up! Titanic Titanic ! Name one song from Beyonce’s album Lemonade that isn’t “Formation”. Guess I give up! Pray You Catch Me Hold Up Don’t Hurt Yourself Sorry 6 Inch Six Inch Daddy Lessons Love Drought Sandcastles Forward Freedom All Night “Pray You Catch Me”, “Hold Up”, “Don’t Hurt Yourself”, “Sorry”, “6 Inch”, “Daddy Lessons”, “Love Drought”, “Sandcastles”, “Forward”, “Freedom”, or “All Night”! What is the name of the youngest Kardashian? Guess I give up! Dream Dream Kardashian Dream Kardashian! Anwar is the little brother of two models. Can you name one of them? Guess I give up! Gigi Gigi Hadid Bella Bella Hadid Gigi and Bella Hadid! Which brand has had collaborations with the likes of Rihanna, Kylie Jenner, and The Weeknd? Guess I give up! Puma Puma! Who was billionaire James Packer previously engaged to? Guess I give up! Mariah Mariah Carey Mariah Carey! Hollywood actor Jake has starred in movies such as Brokeback Mountain , Southpaw , and Nightcrawler . But how do you spell his last name? Guess I give up! Gyllenhaal Jake Gyllenhaal! What is the name of the song that was used for the mannequin challenge? Guess I give up! Black Beatles “Black Beatles”! Prince Harry is dating Meghan Markle. Which TV show is she currently a part of? Guess I give up! Suits Suits ! Fifty Shades of Grey and Fifty Shades Darker are two parts of the Fifty Shades trilogy, but what is the name of the third instalment? Guess I give up! Fifty Shades Freed Freed 50 Shades Freed Fifty Shades Freed ! Who is the common link between TV shows Grey’s Anatomy , Scandal , and How To Get Away With Murder ? Guess I give up! Shonda Rhimes Shonda Shonda Rhimes! Which Nickelodeon TV show did Ariana Grande first find fame on? Guess I give up! Victorious Victorious ! Who tweeted the following: “Does anyone think global warming is a good thing? I love Lady Gaga. I think she’s a really interesting artist.” Guess I give up! Britney Spears Britney Britney Spears! Can You Beat This Infuriating Pop Culture Quiz? Pop culture novice! You don’t really know that much about pop culture. You might like certain songs, TV shows, or movies, but you don’t actually know much about them, and your celebrity knowledge is just as bad.
Pop culture amateur! You got a fair amount of questions right on this quiz, but you didn’t quite have the knowledge to get them all right. You are a fan of pop culture though, you’re just a bit iffy on the specifics.
Pop culture nerd! You’re pretty obsessed with all things pop culture and are very knowledgable about a lot of different aspects. You didn’t score full marks, but you did a pretty good job.
Pop culture expert! You basically know all there is to know when it comes to pop culture. You’re up-to-date on what’s happening now, and your knowledge about things that have happened in the past is just as solid.
SHARE YOUR RESULTS ID: 10575313
Ben Henry is a staff writer for BuzzFeed UK and is based in London.
